headline: VIAVI Closes Acquisition of Spirent Communications plc's High-Speed Ethernet, Network Security and Channel Emulation Testing Business
summary: VIAVI Solutions Inc. (VIAVI) (NASDAQ: VIAV) today announced that it has completed the acquisition of Spirent Communications plc's high-speed ethernet, network security and channel emulation testing business (collectively, the "HSE, Network Security and CE Business") from Keysight Technologies, Inc.
